name: Paris Christmas Shit
description:
On the evening of December 24, 2021,
the magic of Christmas operates in the streets of Paris. through this immortalized moment.

On November 24, 1883, under the Third Republic, the Prefect of the Seine, Eugène Poubelle, signed a prefectural decree relating to the removal of household waste, to fight against the accumulation of waste in the streets of Paris
